<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cold-adj">cold <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kəʊld/    美 /koʊld/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>冷的；寒冷的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 hot / warm </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>cold weather
寒冷的天气</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It <strong>turned cold</strong> that night.
那天夜里天变冷了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The room <strong>felt ice / freezing cold</strong>. Would you please turn on the heating? 
屋里感觉冷极了，把暖气打开好吗？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>冷淡的；冷漠的：</strong></h4>
<p>反 warm </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a cold look
冰冷的表情</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A few minutes later, the headmaster walked towards the couple with a cold face.
几分钟后，校长一脸冷漠地走向那对夫妇。</p></div></div>